---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profilePhoto from '../assets/profile.svg';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 bg-zinc-900 fade-section">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-10 text-center">
      About Me
    </h2>

    <!-- Profile photo -->
    <div
      class="rounded-full overflow-hidden w-[200px] h-[200px] flex-shrink-0 border-[3px] border-[#f7dd30] mb-10"
      style="box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);"
    >
      <Image
        src={profilePhoto}
        alt="Goran Ljiljak"
        width={200}
        height={200}
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Bio text -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed text-center max-w-[700px]">
      <p>
        I am a Power BI Developer and Data Consultant based in Novi Sad, Serbia, with over 10 years
        of experience working across data, reporting, and business systems. Like a certain Caped
        Crusader, I work best in the dark — dark mode dashboards, dark backgrounds, and
        dark-themed everything.
      </p>
      <p>
        My focus is on turning complex data into clear, actionable reports and dashboards that help
        businesses make better decisions. I specialise in Power BI report development and service
        administration, data modelling, and building reporting solutions that people actually use.
        No sidekick required.
      </p>
      <p>
        My background spans the full data stack — from SAP ERP systems and SQL databases, through
        data engineering with Python and Google Cloud Platform, to front-end reporting in Power BI.
        That combination lets me understand a business problem at every layer, from the raw data
        source to the executive dashboard. Consider me your data's World's Greatest Detective.
      </p>
      <p>
        I am fluent in Serbian, English, and German, which allows me to work effectively with
        international teams and clients across Europe.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are looking for someone to build, improve, or take ownership of your Power BI
        reporting — let's connect. The Bat-Signal is always on.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
